data.description: Are you looking for a small town living? Come check out this 3 bedroom with a 4th non conforming room, 1 3/4 bath, decent sized backyard, and with plenty of opportunities to put your own spin inside the home. The home includes a new washer, dryer, refrigerator, and brand new a/c unit. Don't miss out on this opportunity today. All information is gathered from sellers or public records.
